suggestedFix:
Replace OnInitialized with:
  protected override async Task OnInitializedAsync() => await LoadDataAsync();

  private async Task LoadDataAsync()
  {
      _isLoading = true;
      _errorMessage = null;
      try
      {
          _players = PlayerRepository.GetByTeamId(Guid.Empty);
          _totals = StatsService.GetTeamTotals(_players);
          _averages = StatsService.GetTeamAverages(_players);
      }
      catch (Exception ex) { _errorMessage = ex.Message; }
      finally { _isLoading = false; }
  }
Also add _isLoading and _errorMessage fields, and conditionally render an error/spinner in the markup.
